  <para style="h">Firemooni</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri Firemooni</para>
  <para style="toc2">Firemooni</para>
  <para style="toc3">Fir</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri</para>
  <para style="mt1">Firemooni</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Pawulo Omutukuvu ye yawandiika ebbaluwa eno wakati w’emyaka <char style="sc">ad</char> 58 ne 64, ng’agiwandiikira Firemooni. Firemooni ono yabeeranga mu kibuga Kkolosaayi. Yali musajja mugagga nnyo era nga mwatiikirivu nnyo mu kibuga omwo. Yali Mukristaayo mumanyifu ddala, nga Pawulo ye yamubuulira n’amutuusa ku kukkiriza Kristo. Mu nnyumba ye Abakristaayo b’omu Kkolosaayi mwe baakuŋŋaaniranga. Omuddu wa Firemooni ayitibwa Onesimo, yali amutoloseeko, ng’addukidde ddala n’atuuka ne mu Ruumi. Eyo gye yasisinkana Pawulo. Pawulo n’amubuulira Enjiri era n’akkiriza Kristo. Mu bbaluwa eno, Pawulo asaba Firemooni azzeeyo Onesimo ewuwe, nga bw’amunnyonnyola nti ku mulundi guno tajja kumuzzaayo ng’omuddu obuddu, wabula ng’owooluganda mu Kristo. N’amutegeeza nti Onesimo (amakulu nti “ow’omugaso”) atabadde wa mugaso mu biseera ebiyise, kaakano ajja kubeera wa mugaso eri Firemooni era n’eri Ekkanisa (lunny. <char style="xt"><ref loc="PHM 1:11">11</ref></char>).</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 9, 23; <ref loc="EPH 3:1">Bef 3:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 1:1">2Ko 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 2:25">Baf 2:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Pawulo, omusibe wa Kristo Yesu, n’owooluganda Timoseewo, tuwandiikira ggwe Firemooni, mukozi munnaffe omwagalwa, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:17">Bak 4:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:25">Baf 2:25</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:5">Bar 16:5</ref></char></note>ne Apofiya mwannyinaffe, ne Alukipo mulwanyi munnaffe, n’Ekkanisa yonna ekuŋŋaanira mu nnyumba yo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ekisa n’emirembe ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo bibeerenga nammwe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Okusaba n’okwebaza</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:8">Bar 1:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Bulijjo bwe mba nga nkusabira neebaza Katonda, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:15">Bef 1:15</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:4">Bak 1:4</ref></char></note>kubanga buli kiseera mpulira nga bw’olina okwagala n’okukkiriza eri Mukama waffe Yesu n’eri abatukuvu bonna. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nsaba nti nga bw’ogenda otegeeza abantu okukkiriza kwo, nabo kubanyweze mu bulamu bwabwe, nga bategeerera ddala ebirungi byonna ebiri mu ffe ku bwa Kristo. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 7:4">2Ko 7:4</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 7:13">13</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 20</char></note>Nsanyuka nnyo era ne nziramu amaanyi olw’okwagala kwo, kubanga emitima gy’abatukuvu giziddwa buggya ku lulwo owooluganda.</para>
  <para style="s1">Pawulo yeegayiririra Onesimo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Noolwekyo newaakubadde era, nga nnina obuvumu mu Kristo, nga nandisobodde okukulagira okukola ekyo ky’osaanira okukola, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 1, 23</char></note>naye okwagala kwange gy’oli kumpaliriza okukusaba obusabi, nze, Pawulo, kaakano akaddiye, era ali mu kkomera olwa Kristo Yesu; <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:15">1Ko 4:15</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:9">Bak 4:9</ref></char></note>nkwegayirira ku bikwata ku mwana wange Onesimo gwe nayamba okukkiriza Mukama waffe nga ndi mu njegere, mu busibe, <verse number="11" style="v"/>Onesimo oyo, gye buvuddeko ataali wa mugaso gy’oli, naye kaakano nga wa mugaso nnyo gye tuli ffembi, <verse number="12" style="v"/>gwe naaweereza gy’oli nga n’omutima gwange gujjirako, <verse number="13" style="v"/>oyo gwe nandyagadde okwesigaliza, ampeereze nga ndi mu busibe olw’enjiri, mu kifo kyo mwe wandibadde onnyambira, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 9:7">2Ko 9:7</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:2">1Pe 5:2</ref></char></note>naye ne saagala kukikola nga tonzikirizza. Saagala okole eky’ekisa olwokubanga oteekwa, wabula kikole lwa kweyagalira. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Kiyinzika okuba nga Onesimo yakwawukanako okumala akaseera, oluvannyuma alyoke abeere naawe ebbanga lyonna, <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 23:8">Mat 23:8</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:2">1Ti 6:2</ref></char></note>nga takyali muddu buddu, naye ng’asingako awo, ng’afuuse owooluganda omwagalwa ennyo, na ddala gye ndi. Kaakano ajja kubeera wa mugaso nnyo gy’oli mu mubiri ne mu Mukama waffe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 8:23">2Ko 8:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Obanga ddala ndi munno, mwanirize mu ngeri y’emu nga bwe wandinnyanirizza singa nze mbadde nzize. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Obanga waliwo ekintu ekibi kye yakukola, oba ekintu ky’omubanja, kimbalirweko. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Kino nkiwandiika mu mukono gwange nze, Pawulo, nti ndikusasula. Sijja kukugamba nti olina ebbanja lyange. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7</char></note>Munnange owooluganda, nkolera ekikolwa kino ekiraga okwagala, omutima gwange guddemu amaanyi mu Kristo. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 2:3">2Ko 2:3</ref></char></note>Nkuwandiikidde ebbaluwa eno nga neesigira ddala nga kye nkusaba ojja kukikola n’okusingawo! <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 1:25">Baf 1:25</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:24">2:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 1:11">2Ko 1:11</ref></char></note>Nninayo n’ekirala kye nkusaba; nkusaba ontegekere we ndisula, kubanga nnina essuubi, nga Katonda okusaba kwammwe ajja kukuddamu anzikirize nkomewo gye muli.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Okusiibula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 1:7">Bak 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Epafula, musibe munnange olw’okubuulira Enjiri ya Kristo Yesu, abalamusizza.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 12:12">Bik 12:12</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 19:29">Bik 19:29</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 4:14">Bak 4:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ne bakozi bannange bano: Makko, ne Alisutaluuko, ne Dema, ne Lukka nabo babalamusizza.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 4:22">2Ti 4:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ekisa kya Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo kibeerenga n’omwoyo gwammwe.</para>
